notes:
Track #3 contains elements of a speech by Bobby Seale. It also contains a sample of the recording "Hospital Prelude Of Love Theme" by Willie Hutch. 
Track #5 contains a sample of the recording "Uphill Peace Of Mind: by Kid Dynamite. It also contains a sample of the recording "If This World Were Mine" by The Bar-Kays. It also contains excerpts from Rick James "Live At Long Beach, CA".

Track #8 contains interpolations of "Too Legit To Quit" by MC Hammer.
